MyBroadband is South Africa’s most powerful B2B marketing platform for IT and telecommunications companies. This is thanks to its position as the largest IT publication in the country – reaching 3 million IT decision makers and tech enthusiasts each month. This influential audience includes: These readers are key decision makers in their companies and are responsible for selecting which IT and telecommunications products their business will use. As a result, companies which partner with MyBroadband to reach its audience have seen significant increases in brand awareness and new sign-ups. MyBroadband makes it easy for companies to reach its audience through innovative marketing products – including sponsored content, social media promotions, videos, and newsletters. It has excellent targeting to reach the right audience, like CEOs, CIOs, CTOs, or IT managers. Companies simply say which audience they want to reach, and MyBroadband does the rest. For more information, contact MyBroadband Sales Director Cara Muller on cara@mybroadband.co.za